message.text:
𝐇𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐒𝐡𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐛𝐮𝐠𝐬! 📸

Ready to show the world through your own lens? This is your time to showcase your skills in the 𝗧𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗺 𝗣𝗵𝗼𝘁𝗼𝗴𝗿𝗮𝗽𝗵𝘆 competition for World Tourism Day 2025!

Join now and be ready to encapsulate the theme of World Tourism Day 2025 entitled “𝗘𝗺𝗽𝗼𝘄𝗲𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗩𝗼𝗹𝘂𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗲𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗺 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗮 𝗧𝗿𝗮𝗻𝘀𝗳𝗼𝗿𝗺𝗮𝘁𝗶𝘃𝗲 𝗧𝗼𝘂𝗿𝗶𝘀𝗺 𝗙𝘂𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗲” through your snaps! 

Don't forget to check out the mechanics and rubrics below. We can't wait to see the world of transformative tourism through your eyes! 

Starting Date: September 10
End Date: September 18

Registration Link:
https://tinyurl.com/4cz27d67
https://tinyurl.com/4cz27d67

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

message.text:
𝐇𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐒𝐡𝐮𝐭𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐛𝐮𝐠𝐬! 📸

Don't forget to check out the mechanics and rubrics below. We can't wait to see the world of transformative tourism through your eyes! 

Starting Date: September 10
End Date: September 18

Registration Link:
https://tinyurl.com/4cz27d67

message.text:
Forge onward, JPIAns!

The Associates Search 2025 welcomes you to lead and connect with your fellow JPIAns. Take this opportunity to enhance your Tamaraw journey. Become one of the knights, the associates of the Far Eastern University Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants, for this school year!

Step into your role as:

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

Let your skills be known and become part of FEU-JPIA Manila’s family by registering through the link below:
https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!

#AssociateSearch2025
#TamHunt2025
#FEUJPIA2526

message.text:
Forge onward, JPIAns!

The Associates Search 2025 welcomes you to lead and connect with your fellow JPIAns. Take this opportunity to enhance your Tamaraw journey. Become one of the knights, the associates of the Far Eastern University Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants, for this school year!

Step into your role as:

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

Let your skills be known and become part of FEU-JPIA Manila’s family by registering through the link below:
https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!

#AssociateSearch2025
#TamHunt2025

actors.name: FEU Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants

message.text:
Forge onward, JPIAns!

The Associates Search 2025 welcomes you to lead and connect with your fellow JPIAns. Take this opportunity to enhance your Tamaraw journey. Become one of the knights, the associates of the Far Eastern University Manila - Junior Philippine Institute of Accountants, for this school year!

Step into your role as:

• Project Associates
• Speakers and Writers' Associates
• Corporate Relations Associates
• Cybermasters Associates
• Talent Associates
• Athletics Associates

Let your skills be known and become part of FEU-JPIA Manila’s family by registering through the link below:
https://bit.ly/AssociatesSearch2025

The registration is open until September 20, 2025 (Saturday) at 10:00 PM.

Note: The registration is open to BS in Accountancy and BS in Internal Auditing students from all year levels.

Wear the mantle of leadership and walk through thy happy halls with JPIAn spirit!

#AssociateSearch2025
#TamHunt2025
#FEUJPIA2526
